<TITLE> More shuffles in admin </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Jan 14 (bdnews24.com)  A day after a major reshuffle in the administration, the government made more changes at the deputy secretary level on Wednesday. Deputy secretary Rafiqul Islam, who was Bureau of Statistics director on deputation, has been made the private secretary to the water resources minister. Deputy secretaries Nurul Islam and Joinal Abedin of defence will be OSDs at the ministry of establishment. Nurul Islam has been deputed to the social welfare ministry as director of 'Service for Children at Risk'. Director of posts and telecommunication Mohammad Shamsul Kibria will be deputy secretary at the communication ministry. Deputy secretary to the communications ministry Dr Aftabun Nahar Maksuda has been transferred to the telecommunications ministry. bdne
